‘ “Labuan business activity” has the meaning 
assigned  to  it  in  the  Labuan  Business  Activity 
Tax Act  1990  [Act  445];

(a)  “Labuan  Offshore  Business  Activity  Tax  Act 
1990”  is  construed  as  reference  to  “Labuan 
Business Activity  Tax Act  1990”;

(b)  “Labuan Offshore Financial Services Authority” 
is construed as reference to “Labuan Financial 
Services Authority”;

(d)  “Offshore Companies Act 1990” is construed as 
reference  to  “Labuan  Companies  Act  1990”; 
